Java EE, Angular 4, Spring, Hibernate, HTML5, CSS/SASS, Git, Jenkins, Unix, industrialisation logicielle, TDD/BDD, Kanban, Lean, Scrum, …
Drupal 8/Symfony 3, PHP7, serveur Apache 2.4, PostgreSQL, Apache Solr 6, Jitsi VideoBridge, FranceConnect, API.ai, Paybox, Sage, Training Orchestra, Message Business
Lieux : Paris, Nantes, Lyon (France), Barcelone (Espagne) ou Hanoi (Vietnam).

